title: Apple sells blockbuster 13 million iPhone 6s, 6s Plus units in launch weekend
content:
(33 minutes ago)  

Apple's new iPhone 6s and iPhone 6s Plus are off to a record breaking start, selling more than 13 million units in their first three days of availability, the company announced on Monday. » View on web
